    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model demonstrates adequate fidelity for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all evaluated operating points. The credibility assessment supports regulatory submission.",
